{"tid":1970240,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"黑警填色大賽 作品集 （未截止 繼續徵稿）","createTime":"2020-04-13T04:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T03:49:04.000Z","uid":217816,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"538371b268b99d0d28bf4056da06e12460841fb8","tid":1970240,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"話說黑警搞左個懶温情既濕鳩填色比賽 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFhR3ap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFhR3ap.jpg&h=1a8ed02f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑警緊係填黑色啦<br />\nPopo page 都唔執輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmZpDJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmZpDJH.jpg&h=abe1a53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係香港黑警 page 個post既留言作品精選<br />\n一齊欣賞<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWakb1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWakb1d.jpg&h=486e7428&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Cot5me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Cot5me.jpg&h=ffb9a111&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDvL7zA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDvL7zA.jpg&h=ec0c5fd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffqTw7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffqTw7b.jpg&h=343482c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPWSNE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPWSNE4.jpg&h=5a7e8d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎以share 圖link形式<br />\n放埋落班狗個page果個19填色post度留言 等更多人欣賞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEvXejk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi